      "code": "PX520507",
      "abbreviation": "PX520507",
      "description": "The Comprehensive Marijuana Motives Questionnaire (CMMQ) Short Form includes 15 self-administered items. Each item is scored on a five-point Likert-style scale ranging from 1 (almost never/never) to 5 (almost always/always).",
