  "translations": {
    "en": {
      "lk_opt_1": "Almost Never/Never",
      "lk_opt_2": "Some of the time",
      "lk_opt_3": "Half of the time",
      "lk_opt_4": "Most of the time",
      "lk_opt_5": "Almost Always/Always",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_because_it_is_there": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? Because it is there",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_to_help_sleep": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? To help you sleep",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_didnt_want_only_not_doing": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? Because you didn't want to be the only one not doing it",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_pain_relief": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? For pain relief",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_see_what_felt_like": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? To see what it felt like",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_forget_problems": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? To forget your problems",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_enjoy_effects": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? To enjoy the effects of it",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_improve_symptoms_manage_health_problem": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? To improve symptoms or manage the effects of a health problem",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_because_want_something_todo": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? Because you wanted something to do",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_because_relaxes_when_in_insecure_situation": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? Because it relaxes you when you are in an insecure situation",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_because_were_drunk": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons?  Because you were drunk",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_replace_use_another_drug_medication": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? To replace the use of another drug or medication",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_because_special_occasion": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? Because it was a special occasion",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_because_safer_than_drinking": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? Because it is safer than drinking alcohol",
      "motives_alcohol_tobacco_and_other_substances_cannabis_can_look_at_world_differently": "Thinking of all the times you have used marijuana, how often would you say that you use for each of the following reasons? So you can look at the world differently"
    }
